<p><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">《温暖的氛围:5分钟建立信任》</span></strong></span></p>
➜［周末映画］香港影史无法超越的25个惊艳瞬间
http://www.sohu.com/a/426941794_167342	7320
<p>「 </p>
<p><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">周末映画</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">On the weekend</span></p>
<p>」 </p>
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/4b7cba8a03e04d749f03cdff10421867.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">01</span></strong></span></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">祖贤穿衣</span></strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/267569cf5eb143698e101b5a0cfdb7b2.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《倩女幽魂》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>王祖贤饰演的聂小倩，</span></p>
<p><span>洗完澡后出浴穿衣，</span></p>
<p><span>长发飘飘一甩头间，</span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><span>眼眸流转，柔媚入骨，</span></p>
<p><span>这哪是鬼，分明是仙女。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>02</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">青霞喝酒</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/16b4978befa5457c95344f7190f778bf.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">《笑傲江湖2：东方不败》</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
<p><span>林青霞女扮男装，</span></p>
<p><span>披着青丝一袭红衣，</span></p>
<p><span>在水中饮酒一幕，</span></p>
<p><span>至今堪称经典。</span></p>
<p><span>此时，</span></p>
<p><span>她既是俊朗的豪气少侠，</span></p>
<p><span>也是妩媚的妖娆少女。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>03</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">淑贞咬牌</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/04198b8a87504b8285e68ce2bde91b17.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">《赌神2》</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
<p><span>邱淑贞一袭红衣亮相，</span></p>
<p><span>坐在赌桌上双腿一收，</span></p>
<p><span>将纸牌轻轻叼在嘴上，</span></p>
<p><span>这一瞬间不知倾倒了多少影迷。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>04</span></strong></span></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">朱茵眨眼</span></strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/d0c5e35ab61d4f9fb799adebc5b5e2e6.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">《大话西游之大圣娶亲》</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
<p><span>朱茵扮演的紫霞仙子，</span></p>
<p><span>对至尊宝眨眼的一瞬间，</span></p>
<p><span>惊艳了时光，</span></p>
<p><span>她清澈明亮的眼睛里，</span></p>
<p><span>既有俏皮，也有妩媚，</span></p>
<p><span>还充满了期待和幸福。</span></p>
<p><span>朱茵之后，再无紫霞。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>05</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">之琳凝视</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/29435d453f3042ce9606dfa3d4f19bdb.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《黄飞鸿之壮志凌云》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>关之琳饰演十三姨。</span></p>
<p><span>是最美十三姨，</span></p>
<p><span>她不施粉黛，</span></p>
<p><span>只需涂个口红，</span></p>
<p><span>就能艳压群芳，</span></p>
<p><span>一个凝视，</span></p>
<p><span>将少女心思展现得淋漓尽致。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>06</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">雅芝拂袖</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/9909b6a5b2384a6ea61879f81062ef0e.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《新白娘子传奇》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>一说起赵雅芝，</span></p>
<p><span>大家立马就会想到《新白娘子传奇》。</span></p>
<p><span>她在剧中的拂袖镜头堪称经典，</span></p>
<p><span>将女性的温柔秀美演到了极致。</span></p>
<p><span>所以，很多人说： </span></p>
<p><span>“赵雅芝之后再无白娘子。”</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>07</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">张敏回眸</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="//p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/03455945ee0f4f64b1e57a6fb1aa519b.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《倚天屠龙记之魔教教主》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>张敏饰演的赵敏，</span></p>
<p><span>身骑白马，蓦然回眸，</span></p>
<p><span>冲着张无忌淡淡一笑。</span></p>
<p><span>这个惊鸿一瞥，</span></p>
<p><span>不仅令张无忌怦然心动，</span></p>
<p><span>更让万千影迷元神出窍。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>08</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">曼玉展颜</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/df2995fa1edb42fb9efdcedd1e6ce7cd.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《甜蜜蜜》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>张曼玉和黎明，</span></p>
<p><span>最后在街头偶遇，</span></p>
<p><span>张曼玉慢慢绽放笑容的画面，</span></p>
<p><span>实在是太美了，</span></p>
<p><span>真的就像歌里唱的一样：</span></p>
<p><span>“好像花儿开在春风里。”</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>09</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">柏芝撩发</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/7da201ad8e6d48318b7b0ff305262562.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《喜剧之王》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>与尹天仇共度良宵后，</span></p>
<p><span>张柏芝饰演的柳飘飘，</span></p>
<p><span>穿着男式衬衫坐在窗边吹风，</span></p>
<p><span>不经意撩拨随风飘散的长发，</span></p>
<p><span>简直是风华绝代啊！</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>10</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">黎姿褪纱</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/ac147334bb2540a8836377857efcf0b6.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《倚天屠龙记之魔教教主》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>剧中黎姿褪下面纱这一幕，</span></p>
<p><span>实在堪称影史经典。</span></p>
<p><span>她眼波流转，明眸善睐，</span></p>
<p><span>恍如坠入凡间的仙子。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>11</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">洁瑛顾盼</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/4d6bda2836b34b189c2cf91decd0882b.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《万家传说》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>蓝洁瑛在该剧中表演，</span></p>
<p><span>可用八个字来形容：</span></p>
<p><span>“顾盼生姿，流光溢彩。”</span></p>
<p><span>所以，影迷送了她一个绰号：</span></p>
<p><span>“眼睛里藏着星星的女人。”</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>12</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">咏仪持花</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/9be0ae8f7a864c2e899ceae0bd145341.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《国产凌凌漆》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>袁咏仪是1990年香港小姐冠军，</span></p>
<p><span>也是首位蝉联金像奖最佳女主角的演员。</span></p>
<p><span>袁咏仪饰演的角色叫李香琴，</span></p>
<p><span>她跟凌凌漆初见的时候，</span></p>
<p><span>手持玫瑰展颜的那一刻，</span></p>
<p><span>将少女之青涩展现得入木三分，</span></p>
<p><span>实在是太惊艳了。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>13</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">王菲回望</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/79d1a2f9602941b2a7cb93cbb1536c70.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《重庆森林》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>《重庆森林》乃影视经典，</span></p>
<p><span>王菲充满迷幻、梦游色彩的演绎，</span></p>
<p><span>堪称该剧最为惊艳的一笔。</span></p>
<p><span>王菲的这一回眸，</span></p>
<p><span>值得人永远品味。</span></p>
<p><span>那时候的王菲，最王菲。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>14</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">蔼明惊喜</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/97e8b02b5d3948b79a907cfaac327458.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《方世玉2：万夫莫敌》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>郭蔼明饰演的花子，</span></p>
<p><span>听到方世玉的提醒声时，</span></p>
<p><span>露出了惊喜笑容，</span></p>
<p><span>这惊喜这笑容，</span></p>
<p><span>将怀春少女的热烈尽现屏幕。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>15</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">若彤弄须</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/3718d043eec049de96003c619f618f06.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《大内密探零零发》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>李若彤在剧中的男装扮相，</span></p>
<p><span>非常惊艳，</span></p>
<p><span>特别是那两撇小胡子，</span></p>
<p><span>撩人心弦。</span></p>
<p><span>你若以为李若彤只能演王语嫣和小龙女，</span></p>
<p><span>那就错了，</span></p>
<p><span>她还会演撩倒众生的男人。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>16</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">楚红害羞</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/8f52ea81d7f14ef299f39c795489dbdc.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《胡越的故事》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>钟楚红在该剧中，</span></p>
<p><span>饰演了一个叫沈青的越南少女。</span></p>
<p><span>她在剧中害羞的一笑，</span></p>
<p><span>将少女之稚嫩单纯演得淋漓尽致，</span></p>
<p><span>从此引起影坛的关注。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>17</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">嘉欣流泪</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/9e03fd106b7a447fbfeb78952a347c33.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《醉拳3》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>李嘉欣在剧中流泪的片段，</span></p>
<p><span>是香港电影的名场面，</span></p>
<p><span>真是梨花带雨楚楚动人啊！</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>18</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">嘉玲煮面</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/a9374d49fd2a45768178e9bda92a8916.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《大内密探零零发》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>周星驰和刘嘉玲吵架这一段，</span></p>
<p><span>以前没看懂，觉得有点作，</span></p>
<p><span>现在才明白这就是爱情。</span></p>
<p><span>刘嘉玲在剧中有句绝妙台词：</span></p>
<p><span>“你肚子饿不饿？我煮碗面给你吃好不好？”</span></p>
<p><span>每次和周星驰吵架后，</span></p>
<p><span>刘嘉玲都会用柔情的眼神说出这句话，</span></p>
<p><span>之前的面红耳赤，</span></p>
<p><span>都化在一碗热气腾腾的面里了。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>19</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">艳芳对视</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/00efbed4597a46589ecbfb4af39a6cb1.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《胭脂扣》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>梅艳芳凭借这部电影， </span></p>
<p><span>拿下了金像奖、金马奖、金龙奖和亚太影展四料影后。</span></p>
<p><span>她跟张国荣的这一对视戏，</span></p>
<p><span>是剧中之经典桥段。</span></p>
<p><span>真应了影迷们的一句话：</span></p>
<p><span>两人一见面，就是天雷勾地火。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>2</span></strong></span><strong><span>0</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">舒淇打枪</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/9dc7690511164bde8e0cd0cb2ec525b1.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《赌圣3：无名小子》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>舒淇对着张家辉，</span></p>
<p><span>握指成枪，</span></p>
<p><span>“砰”地开了一枪。</span></p>
<p><span>这一枪， </span></p>
<p><span>实在是太美了，</span></p>
<p><span>实在是太性感了，</span></p>
<p><span>实在是太俏皮了。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>21</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">丽珍握耳</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/409d8727f2d144098ce74122934d939f.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《玉蒲团之玉女心经》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>这部电影，</span></p>
<p><span>算是香港情色电影的经典之作，</span></p>
<p><span>由李丽珍和舒淇主演。</span></p>
<p><span>李丽珍这一握耳镜头，</span></p>
<p><span>将女扮男装是“女性”一面，</span></p>
<p><span>偷偷地“泄露”了出来。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>22</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">慧敏不舍</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/e68b657cc1954d8cb0a9eb5472da2a9c.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《风雨同路》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>周慧敏是一代玉女的代名词。</span></p>
<p><span>眼神中不经意流露出的性感，</span></p>
<p><span>又完美诠释了“清纯欲”。</span></p>
<p><span>在《风雨同路》中身着婚纱这一镜头，</span></p>
<p><span>又娇俏又妩媚又清纯，</span></p>
<p><span>谁不对穿婚纱的周慧敏心动呢！</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>23</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">采妮舞剑</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/0f69d928718b465f942a4b4204736eaa.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《七剑》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>玉女杨采妮，</span></p>
<p><span>在《七剑》中扮演武元英。</span></p>
<p><span>她所用的是一把酷剑，</span></p>
<p><span>能伸能缩，两头共用。</span></p>
<p><span>为了使好这把剑，</span></p>
<p><span>杨采妮吃尽苦头，</span></p>
<p><span>并多次负伤，</span></p>
<p><span>才终于演出了女侠的飒爽之气。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>24</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">美玲撒娇</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/7ef5ffd97643476097dd01a2017bcc70.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《射雕英雄传》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>《射雕英雄传》被翻拍多次，</span></p>
<p><span>而古灵精怪聪明绝顶的黄蓉，</span></p>
<p><span>自然也被很多女星饰演过，</span></p>
<p><span>但最经典的还是翁美玲版。</span></p>
<p><span>在绝大多数观众心中，</span></p>
<p><span>黄蓉就是翁美玲，</span></p>
<p><span>翁美玲就是黄蓉，</span></p>
<p><span>别人是在演黄蓉，</span></p>
<p><span>而翁美玲则根本就是黄蓉。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>25</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">咏琪抿嘴</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/b9c29c7ac9ab4ee097cc6ccf5ee34584.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>《爱上百分百英雄》</span></strong><span></span></p>
<p><span>若瑄抽烟、咏琪抿嘴，</span></p>
<p><span>出自电影《爱上百分百英雄》。</span></p>
<p><span>那时候的徐若瑄和梁咏琪，</span></p>
<p><span>真是清纯无敌，美到极致。</span><span></span></p>
<p><span><strong>摄诗书店今日好书推荐</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">只为女人拍电影：沟口健二的世界</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201024/f39eb6fb12f1404c8d50dcde6b129ee3.jpeg" /></p>
